signature. It was alarmed by an attempt at hacking. It sent a power surge on 
the panel where it was originated to block it. It then locked down its 
systems only to dark mouse. With no way to override it. It locked onto the 
troops entered and sent numerous fires at megs forces as the autoguns lowered 
from the walls. (10 in all.)
